l":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2Cj","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e077ab1090564e6714fc0dc395d40985?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e077ab1090564e6714fc0dc395d40985?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e077ab1090564e6714fc0dc395d40985?s=73&d=retro","created":1533946843,"last_modified":1655885028},"last_reply_by":"msdurex","last_touched":1710986423,"title":"求 macOS 上支持 OCR 的截图软件（类似 qq 截图）","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1025602","created":1710981651,"deleted":0,"content":"目前在用 xnip 终身版，除了不支持 ocr 都挺好的。\r\n\r\n知道系统带的截图支持 ocr ，但需要手动打开图片再进行文字识别或标记编辑，太麻烦了。\r\n\r\n想求一个类似 qq 截图那样的支持\r\n1. 支持截完图后自动弹出编辑窗口\r\n2. 支持 OCR\r\n\r\n付费方式只要不是订阅制都可以接受～\r\n\r\n\r\n补充一点：\r\n需要支持长截图，之前就是因为这个痛点找到了 xnip 。","content_rendered":"<p>目前在用 xnip 终身版，除了不支持 ocr 都挺好的。</p>\n<p>知道系统带的截图支持 ocr ，但需要手动打开图片再进行文字识别或标记编辑，太麻烦了。</p>\n<p>想求一个类似 qq 截图那样的支持</p>\n<ol>\n<li>支持截完图后自动弹出编辑窗口</li>\n<li>支持 OCR</li>\n</ol>\n<p>付费方式只要不是订阅制都可以接受～</p>\n<p>补充一点：\n需要支持长截图，之前就是因为这个痛点找到了 xnip 。</p>\n","last_modified":1710981848,"replies":23,"id":1025602},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":61864,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269","stars":8899,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":610160,"username":"SmartTom","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/SmartTom","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"苏州","tagline":"你好哈哈","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a593/b233/610160_mini.png?m=1673502156","avat