11","last_touched":1710987247,"title":"Apple M 芯片支持安装 arm 架构的 Linux 虚拟机吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1025605","created":1710982410,"deleted":0,"content":"这几天一直在纠结是不是换 m 系列的 macbook 。\r\n\r\n因为工作的原因，需要使用 x86 和 arm 两种架构的 Linux 。目前是在 mac 上使用 vmware 安装 x86 linux ，在服务器上使用 kvm 安装 arm Linux 。\r\n\r\n如果 Apple M 芯片能在本地安装 arm linux 的虚拟机，就准备入手 m 系列了。\r\n\r\n大家有这方面的经验吗？谢谢。","content_rendered":"<p>这几天一直在纠结是不是换 m 系列的 macbook 。</p>\n<p>因为工作的原因，需要使用 x86 和 arm 两种架构的 Linux 。目前是在 mac 上使用 vmware 安装 x86 linux ，在服务器上使用 kvm 安装 arm Linux 。</p>\n<p>如果 Apple M 芯片能在本地安装 arm linux 的虚拟机，就准备入手 m 系列了。</p>\n<p>大家有这方面的经验吗？谢谢。</p>\n","last_modified":1710982410,"replies":15,"id":1025605},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_large.png?m=1591791660","name":"gts","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_normal.png?m=1591791660","title":"全球工单系统","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/gts","topics":9796,"footer":"","header":"希望这里能够为你遇到的问题找到解决方案","title_alternative":"Global Ticket System","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_mini.png?m=1591791660","stars":1822,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":938,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":247509,"username":"hh4646908","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hh4646908","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6cc8/3fc9/247509_mini.png?m=1536566808","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6cc8/3fc9/247509_normal.png?m=1536566808","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6cc8/3fc9/247509_large.png?m=1536566808","created":1502177152,"last_modified":1536566808},"last_reply_by":"cinhoo","last_touched":1710989145,"title":"深圳四博智联科技 AIYATO 防丢器故障求助 @liqinliqin","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1025651","created":1710987885,"deleted":0,"content":"去年 9 月在 V 站看到的推广 @liqinliqin ，我买了 4 个，推荐朋友每人买了 4 个。半年的使用我们都遇到了无法绑定手机的问题，具体情况是防丢器没电了，未解绑的情况下更换电池，再次开机无法连接，咨询客服，解绑防丢器，重启手机，重置防丢器多次未果，最终客服给出的结论是\r\n\r\n“这个可能是移除设备没有成功 能多复位几次，重启一下手机试一下，再不行隔一段时间再试，只能这样”\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n在这想直接请教深圳四博智联科技研发负责人 @liqinliqin ，这问题如何解决？这不会就是个一次性产品吧？","content_rendered":"<p>去年 9 月在 V 站看到的推广 @<a href=\"/member/liqinliqin\">liqinliqin</a> ，我买了 4 个，推荐朋友每人买了 4 个。半年的使用我们都遇到了无法绑定手机的问题，具体情况是防丢器没电了，未解绑的情况下更换电池，再次开机无法连接，咨询客服，解绑防丢器，重启手机，重置防丢器多次未果，最终客服给出的结论是</p>\n<p>“这个可能是移除设备没有成功 能多复位几次，重启一下手机试一下，再不行隔一段时间再试，只能这样”</p>\n<p>在这想直接请教深圳四博智联科技研发负责人 @<a href=\"/member/liqinliqin\">liqinliqin</a> ，这问题如何解决？这不会就是个一次性产品吧？</p>\n","last_modified":1710988129,"replies":12,"id":1025651},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":216708,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":4128,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":531534,"username":"JeffyChen","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/JeffyChen","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8645ed622f9794bcf7a3926c507620e8?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8645ed622f9794bcf7a3926c507620e8?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8645ed622f9794bcf7a3926c507620e8?s=73&d=retro","created":1612170548,"last_modified":1612170548},"last_reply_by":"coderxy","last_touched":1710989132,"title":"你们会按照保养手册，去保养车子吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1025639","created":1710986540,"deleted":0,"content":"你们会完全按照保养手册，该换的换，该保养的保养吗？","content_rendered":"<p>你们会完全按照保养手册，该换的换，该保养的保养吗？</p>\n","last_modified":1710986540,"replies":12,"id":1025639},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea